com.moniuliuma.fingerprint

Class FingerprintManagerCompat

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.moniuliuma.fingerprint.FingerprintManagerCompat

  • public final class FingerprintManagerCompat
extends java.lang.Object
    Class represents a main access point to the Fingerprint hardware device Java SDK library. This class contains a set of static factory methods, which allow user to access capture and engine interfaces of the SDK.
